WEBVTT

00:00:00.787 --> 00:00:02.588
Al Gore: Hello everyone, I'm Al Gore,

00:00:02.612 --> 00:00:06.396
founder and chairman
of the Climate Reality Project.

00:00:06.420 --> 00:00:10.136
This extraordinary moment
of great challenge and great loss

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:13.246
is obviously also a moment
of great awakening

00:00:13.270 --> 00:00:15.470
and a great opportunity.

00:00:15.890 --> 00:00:17.318
The global pandemic,

00:00:17.342 --> 00:00:21.756
structural and institutional racism,
with its horrific violence,

00:00:21.780 --> 00:00:24.136
the worsening impacts
of the climate crisis --

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:26.427
all of these have
accelerated the emergence

00:00:26.451 --> 00:00:30.746
of a new and widespread
collective understanding